paragraph
 HyperCard was a piece of application software and a programming tool for Apple Macintosh and Apple IIGS computers. It was among the first successful hypermedia systems before the World Wide Web. HyperCard combined a flat-file database with a graphical, flexible, user-modifiable interface. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HyperCard">Read more on Wikipedia...</a>

